ygData.subject: Re: Welcome to eqenchanters@onelist.com
ygData.msgSnippet: Twinked refers to a charecter who has been given stuff instead of earning it themselves.  Usually this is another char of the same player. Purchases and trades
ygData.messageBody:
Twinked refers to a charecter who has been given stuff instead of earning it
themselves. Usually this is another char of the same player.
Purchases and trades don't count as twinking but someone who gives you
something valuable aobve what you ahve earned does.
Stonedreamer of Fenin Ro
Refplace Hosting services
www.refplace.com
www.eqportal.com
